ConvertableLengthUnit - Interface in com.github.emabrey.javartmp.core.measurement.length
This interface allows the implementation of the LengthRange class with an automatic unit conversion capability that can convert between units using an accuracy of one whole byte and a maximum size of ULong.MAX_VALUE; the maximum size is limited only by the maximum size of the unsigned long primitive.
